content: What a week! So strange and fascinating this life I live. Mother's Day I, for a brief few hours, I stepped  into someone else's nightmare. A mom on #longisland pushed her daughter out of the way of s speeding car. Mom was killed but saved her only daughter. Met an amazing couple in #coneyisland , stray bullet pierced their bedroom window but incredibly they were not hurt. I worked with a true legend in the entertainment work @sirjohnofficial So cool, does makeup for some of the most gorgeous women in the world, #beyonce . Had the honor of meeting legends, #lyndacarter #marlothomas #reginaking #lynnwhitfield. Then today spoke to a mom and daughter nearly killed in #timessquare . Both hit by that speeding car.
